headline: Avis Budget Group Stock Declines 21.8% Since Reporting Q4 Loss
summary: CAR shares plunge 21.8% after Q4 loss of $6.53 per share and revenue miss as Americas sales fall. The 2026 EBITDA guidance ranges from $800M to $1B.
